    {
      "id": "1b34750c-f3ba-80e9-aa97-dec377b6c333",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Most of the work in Learning Analytics focuses on making predictions and not as much in interpreting the causes that lead to a certain prediction, as Explainable AI has only recently become a thing. The work proposes a framework that combines XAI and prescriptive analytics, with the added caveat of having a LLM communicate insights to learners. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1b34750c-f3ba-80e9-aa97-dec377b6c333",
        "parent": {
