    {
      "id": "1b34750c-f3ba-8079-a0ee-dcc866ab3e04",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The authors use a dataset of around 7000 students ranging from 2018 and 2022 meant to identify learners at risk of qualifying in their program. ",
